           public static final String CONST_XRP_TEAM_ITEM_DES3 ="Kristina Campbell is Chief Financial Officer at Ripple. She has over 20 years of experience in finance operations and business strategy with a focus on fintech and payments. Previously, she was CFO at PayNearMe, where both the business and team grew substantially under her leadership. She also held several roles at GreenDot, a now $2.5B public fintech company, including General Manager of GoBank.";
